(* Pure, dual-compiler test basis for sml-serve.

   Unlike ../sources.mlb (which links the impure, socket-bound adapter and its
   loopback integration suite, and is therefore MLton-only), this basis pulls
   in ONLY the pure vendored sml-json chain plus the integer-boundary suite.
   It builds and runs identically under MLton and Poly/ML (via tools/polybuild),
   so its output is byte-identical across both compilers.

   The sml-json sources.mlb brings the vendored sml-parsec core with it, so
   `Json`, `JsonPretty`, and `CharParsec` are all in scope. *)

$(SML_LIB)/basis/basis.mlb

../../lib/github.com/sjqtentacles/sml-json/sources.mlb

../harness.sml
../json_boundary.sml
entry.sml
main.sml
